oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Songwriter Session - Jamie Floyd - 2018-12-16
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by songwriter Jamie Floyd from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on December 16, 2018. Accompanied by Tommy Martin on guitar and Kellie (sic) Floyd.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Jamie Floyd
